{"tid":1840027,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[求解答] 病毒 SIZE VS 邊類口罩防得到? N95 / 外科口罩","createTime":"2020-01-24T16:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T22:54:15.000Z","uid":216683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ada4585da2c223408a331e782f38c4418f1be00e","tid":1840027,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:24:24.000Z","msg":"問題:<br />\n<br />\nSARS病毒大小係 0.14 &micro;m<br />\n<br />\nN95 = 95: 代表隔到 95% 以上 0.3&mu;m 直徑大的粒子<br />\n<br />\n外科口罩<br />\nVFE（ Virus Filtration Efficiency ）從口罩過濾飛沫病毒微粒3.0 &mu;m（微米）的微粒效率<br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦<br />\n<br />\nSARS主要傳播途徑係飛沫<br />\n意思係病毒痴係飛沫上面, SIZE總共有AROUND 4.0&mu;m<br />\n所以D人先會話係SARS期間, <br />\n用N95 同有效用嘅外科口罩個效果係一樣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">假設</span></strong></span><br />\n今次呢隻WARS, 唔再係靠飛沫傳播為途徑<br />\n而係飛沫噴出黎後, 可以係空氣間停留<br />\n咁病毒SIZE係細過哂所有口罩嘅密度, 變相係直入?<br />\n當然, 呢個就會變咗係空氣傳播.....<br />\n<br />\n所以想問, 如果出現情況1, 係咪可以放棄唔洗買罩?"},{"pid":"59f8f2338739ca6d7574d60142688fc3810669ef","tid":1840027,"uid":51068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:25:06.000Z","msg":"[內幕分析] 林奠用萬條人命落賭注，如果醫護市民唔團結，林奠就可以用病毒翻盤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1839427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1839427</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"71b05c997cda2a2672a90815c0aeb2999475a3d7","tid":1840027,"uid":11154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁平時戴黎都要防飛沬?<br />\n同埋微粒傳播好似都唔知會成日出現?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申唔清楚"},{"pid":"166eac7b6bb6dd8bc99e4f36319f267c3361c385","tid":1840027,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"暫時大家都係假設佢係飛沬傳播<br />\n計落佢有4&micro;m, 所以用N95, 又或者用有效嘅外科口罩係一樣!<br />\n(N95防0.3&micro;m以上, 有效外科口罩防3.0&micro;m以上, 當然有個成功 %)<br />\n<br />\n但<br />\n<br />\n只要佢係用新方式傳播<br />\n個SIZE係細過 3.0&micro;m<br />\n咁已經有一堆外科口罩無用<br />\n<br />\n再假設個新方式, SIZE係細過0.3&micro;m, 又或者病毒係直接空氣中(0.14&micro;m)<br />\n咁更加<br />\n連N95, N99, N100 都無用<br />\n<br />\n因為佢只係防到0.3&micro;m以上嘅野...<br />\n<br />\n咁更加解釋得到<br />\n點解王專家, 有帶N95都中?"},{"pid":"4cd24656266109fa2d95237f1ac0a3fbc341bb19","tid":1840027,"uid":41130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:04:08.000Z","msg":"咁出街係咪要用氧氣筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b01b280a93eec84db8ec61a1ee201d4277ba17","tid":1840027,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T21:41:29.000Z","msg":"空氣成功率都唔會100%，你唯有博自己好彩吸少幾粒病毒無咁易奶野"},{"pid":"bc838dbe4fcbb32cc5b6bdb53b95d4f62bfbd57d","tid":1840027,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T21:44:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612777b15a68be21a6493c48a1750500d99d5470","tid":1840027,"uid":25727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71b05c997cda2a2672a90815c0aeb2999475a3d7","tid":1840027,"uid":11154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁平時戴黎都要防飛沬?<br />\n同埋微粒傳播好似都唔知會成日出現?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申唔清楚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T22:02:49.000Z","msg":"戴口罩係為咗當你感染嘅時候可以減低傳染俾其他人嘅機會從而截斷傳染鏈<br />\n同當你出現病徵eg發燒 嘅時候要即時隔離係同一原理<br />\n想要防乜防物嘅就麻煩成套防護衣拎出嚟著"},{"pid":"2e6210e9379cfa38fcb29e21807b330ff87b33e6","tid":1840027,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T22:54:15.000Z","msg":"ASTM Level 3 99% BFE/PFE at 0.1 micron 得唔得？"}]}